HEADWORD: Quebec group
<hw>Que*bec" group`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Geol.)</fld> <def>The
middle of the three groups into which the rocks of the Canadian period
have been divided in the American Lower Silurian system. See the
<xex>Chart</xex> of <er>Geology</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

